snippet.title: CrocApoca!! Crocodile maiden at the End of the World – Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
CrocApoca!! is a comedy/drama heartwarming visual novel. Take care of a cute crocodile girl and make it through the Apocalypse while your bossy step-sister and some mysterious organizations are getting in your way! 



CrocApoca!! on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1294620/CrocApoca_Crocodile_maiden_at_the_End_of_the_World/
Our Twitter - https://twitter.com/flat_chest_dev
